<br>
If you're claiming that you killed P'tasa 23 times before he dropped a staff, I don't believe you.  If you're saying that you killed P'tasa 23 times before you were *awarded* a staff drop, then that's a whole different story.<br>
<br>
All that I claimed is that I don't believe people who say they've killed mobs like P'tasa and Undertow (which have more than a 50% chance of dropping the items) over 20 times without them dropping the item.  If you kill them and don't get to loot it, that's a different story.<br>
<br>
