<br>
When  he does pop, gate ,  and invis swim down  to his  lair. On the ledge before  the  swirlspines and the  star floor,  drop an eye of Tallon  and swim it west  into the hole in the floor.  Eyes dont swim fast but they manage.  Have to use a Eye of Tallon or you wont reach him.  Keep swiming west   to his little alcove in the west wall  and  he will become visiable,  with eye   you can get close enough  to see which which  weapons he is weilding. If he has the Water Staff   in his Inventory   you will see in his hand. He often has the Malisement rod or the rogue peicer thing  or the enchanter mana seive rod.  <br>
<br>
Now  if  he doesnt  have the staff visable  leave him up and  go about your buisiness. Let someone else kill him.  If you have your  /hidden tracker there this is ideal , because,  you will know exactly  when he dies.  Can log off tracker and return  12 hours later.( be sure to  hook  tracker up with  a fishbobe earring or something of that nature for EB)   Swim down  once he repops again and check if he is holding staff again.   Once he does have the staff on him finally  you only have to kill him once.<br>
<br>
Making it very easy to  get help  on this this phish  if you leave tracker there grouped ( at zone in)with you (the mage)  to invite for CoH's  down to his lair.  This way  your help doesnt get burned out front  helping  you kill him 20+times.  With this method  it should only  take  1 kill.  <br>
<br>
I started  out by   just flat camping him with tracker.   then  mobilize once he is up...    The method i mentioned above is far easier and  less annoying than   killing  time after time.  <br>
<br>
Will also  say  that  phinny's room and him, are do able  by 3 mages and a cleric as well.   As mages on my server band together to take out epic mobs in very low numbers( why would you group with anyone BUT mages?)<br>
<br>
Hope  you use this method  to your advantage and let the other  guilds/groups  kill him sencelessly,  while  you waltz in  when  he finally does spawn with  your staff.. Good Luck  <br>
<br>
Master Roinin Pyrefists<br>
