<br>
Personally, I've killed the Magi 7 times, seen the staff drop once.  I'm up to 27 Hate raids.  So far, I've seen no evidence of a 50% drop rate.<br>
<br>
A casual player cannot really expect to finish this quest.  The Quill cloak can be bought, but the other bottlenecks have stymied me.  No guild I know has plans to do the 7th isle of Air.. there's just no percentage in it for them, since the only reason to go there is for the crown.  I've never heard or seen an Air Crown MQ for sale on my server, so my chances of buying it are near zero.<br>
<br>
Also, with the number of the guilds on my server going FFA on raid mobs and planes over the last few weeks, the chances I'll be able to see the Magi up are lessening rapidly.  He's gone within 60 minutes of repop usually.  I can't compete with that.<br>
<br>
I could change guilds, but I like my guild, and I really don't want to change just for a quest.<br>
<br>
So, my struggle is over.  I officially told my guild that I was done with the epic as of this last weekend.  I've given up.  I'll level to 61 and work on my PoP pets instead.<br>
<br>
Good luck to the rest of you.  <br>
<br>
